1.0 - Monday 30 January 2006
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

- Fixed an unreported bug where in the case of an uncaught exception the error
  handler's onError() method would be called twice.


